This paper deals with action description languages and their formalization using Constraint Logic Programming over Finite Domains. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
